original_title: The Making of the Lumberjack's Daughter
overview: An egotistical filmmaker gets his "friends" to help him make a movie to impress his YouTube idol. This movie was shot and improvised in its entirety in under three hours. It was done during the broadcast of the 95th Academy Awards as part of Joel Haver's "Make a Movies During the Oscars 2023" competition.
title: The Making of the Lumberjack's Daughter
